---
title: Pork Jägerschnitzel & Mushroom Sauce with Potato Mash & Apple Salad
description: Jägerschnitzel, a hearty German delight, pairs tender breaded pork with a rich mushroom sauce that’s perfect for a cosy feast for the adults. Potato mash soaks up extra sauce and acts as the ideal accompaniment for this dreamy combo!
